data.description: Back on the Market 7-31-18: Here is a nicely updated and hard to find 3 bedroom 2 and 1/2 bath home in the desirable Holt Park neighborhood. Fresh paint, fresh carpet, wood grain flooring, brand new stainless steel appliances, a large sitting porch, gas log fireplace, 1st floor laundry and the hidden gem, a finished man cave or craft room above the 2 car garage, this is a feature no other home in Holt Park has. Out back you'll find a extra large backyard with a patio and fire pit. So with a limited supply of homes on the market, this one stands out because it is move in ready for you. Call your agent to schedule an appointment today.
